{"tid":1224291,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人會唔會當11個被捕人士係comdom?","createTime":"2019-06-15T02:51:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T03:05:12.000Z","uid":5809,"like":94,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"063e5f6141f049519671827cb691c7c4c7daf048","tid":1224291,"uid":5809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:51:59.000Z","msg":"條柒婆暫緩啫，隨時一選完立法會拉晒班議員就再推過！！！<br />\n<br />\n而且搞撚咗場大龍鳳無一個官員要負責問責下台？<br />\n<br />\n浪費咗市民咁多人力物力一句暫緩就算？我屌你老母啦！！！<br />\n<br />\n同埋被捕人士為香港犧牲！！！我地唔可以見死不救！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最低限度都要佢地保證不會檢控任何示威者！！！<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1.撤回送中惡法<br />\n2.林鄭及相關官員必須問責下台<br />\n3.釋放所有被捕人士及保證不會檢控任何示威者<br />\n4.起訴6.12涉嫌謀殺示威者及濫用暴力之警員及其上司<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">4樣無一樣野做到，依d叫階段性勝利</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正評：星期日上街迫林鄭下台，釋放義士<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 負評：只有港共畜牲先會負評<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人一個都不能少</span></span>"},{"pid":"94176c7b09dc45a135d7f4a15c8e0184f8cf2230","tid":1224291,"uid":5809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:52:14.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5aa96f1ea6c8a0e6f5d7c3d76b547abb7571415","tid":1224291,"uid":5809,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:53:06.000Z","msg":"係香港人既星期日企出黎，保護返香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cfca1e5b7fd838e3c1a165020a22dadaa3b6596","tid":1224291,"uid":32655,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:53:35.000Z","msg":"1，3 ，4係必須，下唔下台都一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},