e":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:57:29.000Z","msg":"有香港人為咗我地食棍!!!中椒!!!中槍!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n同為咗我地被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地一定要救返佢地，唔可以當佢地係comdom用完即棄！！！"},{"pid":"cf78721d97c7bb252ab9d8f0b0dfb1afece8e645","tid":1224291,"uid":218081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:58:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BpsbqRp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBpsbqRp.jpg&h=fd8e913b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n冇人出聲就冇架喇！通過咗香港就冇將來！<br />\n現在今天不出來，以後永遠都冇機會嫁啦!!!!!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n覺得想幫手又承擔唔到風險的請參加和平的遊行，遊行人數都係好重要的輿論支持<br />\n<br />\n不要因為希望而堅持；<br />\n而係因為堅持才有希望。<br />\n香港加油💪🏻香港人加油💪🏻"},{"pid":"c93abf79935e79cfe3888689c8508c77743a21ea","tid":1224291,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:59:49.000Z","msg":"釋放被捕人士"},{"pid":"f5360f538e774210aeaeb51f83947e1a9e2b1456","tid":1224291,"uid":90743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:00:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"360271e367e2e75706da7a59f6a2c7723e9761ed","tid":1224291,"uid":176313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:00:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>撤回，不僅撤回！<br />\n不撤回不散！<br />\n不放人不散！<br />\n不引咎不散！<br />\n不追責不散！<br />\n<br />\n仲有，不可秋後算賬！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"90dd6efba679890d5868b2f0b1b1759d4afd3dd8","tid":1224291,"uid":5809,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:02:01.000Z","msg":"我地今鋪要做既野係要推倒高牆<br />\n<br />\n係要成幅推冧！！！唔成幅推冧，下一幅只會蓋得更高！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人好耐未試過贏一場政治，今鋪大好機會一定要漂漂亮亮咁贏一場，以後我地先可以照住個模式，搵到出路"},{"pid":"15dbf1d60eedf5af8822c3d16a3565bb40151321","tid":1224291,"uid":5809,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:02:29.000Z","msg":"已經有一隻共狗負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":